eu.fbk.dkm.springles.base

Class ForwardingSpringlesConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • eu.fbk.dkm.springles.base.ForwardingSpringlesConnection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SpringlesConnection, org.openrdf.repository.RepositoryConnection

    public abstract class ForwardingSpringlesConnection
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
implements SpringlesConnection
    Implementation of SpringlesConnection that forwards by default all method calls to a delegate SpringlesConnection.

    This class is modelled after the 'forwarding' pattern of Guava (see ForwardingObject). Subclasses must implement method delegate() which is called by other methods and must provide the delegate SpringlesConnection instance.

    Note that this class does not implement the marker Sesame interface DelegatingRepositoryConnection: it is up to subclasses to decide whether to implement it, thus exposing the fact they are wrappers and providing the capability to change the delegate connection after instantiation. For the same reason this class does not extend RepositoryConnectionWrapper (also for not inheriting from RepositoryBase inderectly through RepositoryConnectionWrapper).
